title: Runaway cow sparks chaos in New York City | The Independent
text:
Runaway cow sparks chaos in New York City Tuesday 21 February 2017 17:37 GMT Click to follow The cow was chased by police through Queens in New York Image via Twitter 
A runaway cow is leading police on a chase through the streets of New York. 
Several police officers and a police car were seen in pursuit of the cow in the Queens area of the city. 
More follows
